specific rules

    1- the config of database is already on .env
    2- follow the sequence:
        1 migrations 
        2 controllers
        3 services
        4 models
        5 requests
        6 front end with vue js using all requests of backend on front-end
        
DATABASE
    start with migrations with these tables
    users
